02-04T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"好明顯係<br />\n<br />\n都話左支那自己自身難保<br />\n又點會幫香港"},{"pid":"0be273306d085c9103da803a26a702bc550467b8","tid":1861173,"uid":82532,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:33:22.000Z","msg":"問下啲CSI去撚咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808acf858e1f84ab01af9b73c6f730cbb67da839","tid":1861173,"uid":102700,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"1e18e7687f0fd0329ae90cef86783f3c141f1b66","tid":1861173,"uid":185045,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"好明顯係<br />\n<br />\n都話左支那自己自身難保<br />\n又點會幫香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"唔好用個幫字<br />\n隻毒係佢地放落黎"},{"pid":"8efad8b71ab6f18b804a979b5ae89ebbead37924","tid":1861173,"uid":33939,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:33:34.000Z","msg":"大陸一日要數以億計嘅口罩，仲俾條毛佢"},{"pid":"867939c5da07cdf9a3a6f5d10a8e063fafcca3d2","tid":1861173,"uid":173598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"大陸開晒口乞緊外國勢力喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"905755ab0d1e20bb39f4b5c834f84b6a6163ea6c","tid":1861173,"uid":21279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"又幾on9先會問個自己都冇錢嘅人拎錢"},{"pid":"8cdc80fae69cc704d5976b120525afea0e6dd9aa","tid":1861173,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"佢唔係做到今日都唔知大陸邊個話事啊？"},{"pid":"e9f42f6d096f5062cb07553320dabac175169d30","tid":1861173,"uid":60872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"講咗林鄭醉翁之意不在酒 只要令人覺得香港無咗中國唔得 同埋中央有同香港共同抗疫 實際有無供應口罩過香港根本唔重要<br />\n<br />\n睇下微博班小粉紅香港&quot;求&quot;中國要口罩就高潮就知林鄭已經達到佢嘅目的"},{"pid":"0176245c1c20951b6f1179f3eccdf3f8f28656a1","tid":1861173,"uid":103363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T04:41:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線先會同支那買<br />\n佢都